title: BNP members: the far right of Britain, UK, 2008
name: BNP members: the far right of Britain, UK, 2008
description: The British National Party (BNP) is a secretive portion of the far right of British politics. Recently a list of the BNPs membership was published online showing the locations and names of all of the members of the BNP. The data is aggregated out to Administrative area centroids, and shows the number of BNP members in each of the areas.
